# Web & mobile conventions

- Keep shared UI and tokens in `packages/ui` and design docs; avoid duplicating components across apps.
- MCP servers under `mcp/` stay thin adapters—no secrets in repo; use env placeholders.
- Follow `docs/00_OPERATOR_LIBRARY/` for PRD-to-repo handover when building new ventures.
